grails (1.3.7-1ubuntu7) lucid; urgency=low

  * Set GROOVY_HOME and GROOVY_VERSION for bash completion script to work.
  * Clean up rules script.
  * Purge changelog of upstream JIRA issues.
  * Bumped debhelper build dependency to 7.0.50~.
  * Change section in control file from devel to java.
  * Move grails from /usr/lib/grails to /usr/share.
  * Added gawk as build dependency for bash completion script.
  * Split package into grails and grails-doc.
  * Lintian tweaks to control file and posinst/prerm scripts.
  * Make grails Suggests: grails-doc
  * Move src/ folder to grails-doc package.
  * Rename patches diff to mnemonic description.

